01:02:36,040 --> 01:02:37,370
Signorina Hirt?

1138
01:02:37,370 --> 01:02:38,290
Yes?

1139
01:02:41,650 --> 01:02:43,270
Signorina [Italian]

1140
01:02:43,370 --> 01:02:44,540
[Italian]

1141
01:02:44,660 --> 01:02:48,900
[Italian]

1142
01:02:49,490 --> 01:02:50,490
Marcello?

1143
01:02:50,860 --> 01:02:51,970
[Italian]

1144
01:02:52,310 --> 01:02:54,510
[Italian]

1145
01:02:54,640 --> 01:02:55,960
Marcello Scalzi.

1146
01:02:56,030 --> 01:02:56,970
Who are you?

1147
01:02:57,110 --> 01:02:59,120
[Italian]

1148
01:02:59,270 --> 01:03:01,670
[Italian]

1149
01:03:01,720 --> 01:03:03,160
[Italian]

1150
01:03:03,310 --> 01:03:04,640
[Italian]

1151
01:03:04,750 --> 01:03:12,400
[Italian]

1152
01:03:12,650 --> 01:03:13,870
[Italian]

1153
01:03:14,190 --> 01:03:16,540
[Italian]

1154
01:03:16,810 --> 01:03:20,850
[Italian]

1155
01:03:28,350 --> 01:03:29,350
Marcello's...

1156
01:03:30,680 --> 01:03:31,950
I don't even know.

1157
01:03:32,400 --> 01:03:33,740
Leave me alone with her.

1158
01:03:35,040 --> 01:03:36,310
I'll handle it.

1159
01:03:42,020 --> 01:03:43,640
Just calm down.

1160
01:03:45,620 --> 01:03:47,830
Per favore si tranquila.

1161
01:03:48,420 --> 01:03:50,850
[Italian]

1162
01:03:53,660 --> 01:03:55,230
It's very embarrassing for me,

1163
01:03:55,230 --> 01:03:57,780
but I have to point out very clearly,

1164
01:03:57,780 --> 01:04:00,350
that it's not allowed to keep dogs in my apartment.

1165
01:04:00,350 --> 01:04:02,070
I don't keep it. It's just for the visit.

1166
01:04:02,070 --> 01:04:04,050
But again and again. That's the fifth time now.

1167
01:04:04,050 --> 01:04:05,130
Sorry,

1168
01:04:05,130 --> 01:04:06,200
but it doesn't do anything.

1169
01:04:06,200 --> 01:04:07,730
The carpets suffer.

1170
01:04:07,870 --> 01:04:10,250
And concerning the rest of the foreign traffic in your room...

1171
01:04:10,260 --> 01:04:12,520
Please don't get worked up unnecessarily. I quit.

1172
01:04:12,520 --> 01:04:13,500
That's just...

1173
01:04:16,110 --> 01:04:17,960
She is Marcello's fiancee.

1174
01:04:18,400 --> 01:04:20,740
But I told her, that you didn't know that...

1175
01:04:21,350 --> 01:04:22,370
What's wrong?

1176
01:04:22,700 --> 01:04:24,190
I just canceled my room.

1177
01:04:24,930 --> 01:04:25,910
Well done!

1178
01:04:25,910 --> 01:04:27,300
You don't need it anymore.

1179
01:04:27,760 --> 01:04:29,580
I have to give you the pleasant news,

1180
01:04:29,580 --> 01:04:33,090
that Kaprun wants to have its Raiffeisen bank executive back.

1181
01:05:42,050 --> 01:05:45,430
... that you're here again.

1182
01:06:13,130 --> 01:06:14,890
Attention. Detonation!

1183
01:06:14,890 --> 01:06:16,380
Full cover!

1184
01:06:19,470 --> 01:06:20,520
[unintelligible dialogue]

1185
01:06:22,020 --> 01:06:23,490
Full cover!

1186
01:07:56,810 --> 01:07:58,240
Miss Angelika.

1187
01:07:59,110 --> 01:08:00,510
Miss Angelika!

1188
01:08:00,510 --> 01:08:01,280
Yes?

1189
01:08:01,500 --> 01:08:04,120
Please let me tell you again privately

1190
01:08:04,220 --> 01:08:07,550
how glad I am, that you returned.

1191
01:08:08,500 --> 01:08:09,870
Thank you, Mr. Zingerl,

1192
01:08:09,950 --> 01:08:12,130
but you told me that yesterday already.

1193
01:08:12,170 --> 01:08:13,960
Yes, this was for the general public.

1194
01:08:13,960 --> 01:08:15,330
Oh, sorry.

1195
01:08:15,750 --> 01:08:17,050
But today,

1196
01:08:17,050 --> 01:08:19,650
Miss Angelika I would like to tell you as...

1197
01:08:19,650 --> 01:08:20,800
regular customer...

1198
01:08:20,970 --> 01:08:22,190
Yes, too.

1199
01:08:22,840 --> 01:08:24,800
But mainly as private person.

1200
01:08:24,800 --> 01:08:26,000
And as that,

1201
01:08:26,100 --> 01:08:27,590
I mean as such,

1202
01:08:27,710 --> 01:08:30,010
I would like to repeat my offer.

1203
01:08:30,010 --> 01:08:30,990
Mr. Zingerl,

1204
01:08:31,040 --> 01:08:32,990
please excuse me for a moment.

1205
01:08:36,870 --> 01:08:38,420
What can I do for you?

1206
01:08:38,520 --> 01:08:40,570
It's about...

1207
01:08:41,090 --> 01:08:43,200
I want to set up a family savings account.

1208
01:08:45,050 --> 01:08:46,060
You want to marry?

1209
01:08:46,070 --> 01:08:46,700
Yes.

1210
01:08:51,500 --> 01:08:53,850
Then fill out this here please.

1211
01:08:54,830 --> 01:08:57,260
First your Name and then your wife's name.

1212
01:08:58,120 --> 01:08:59,100
Bernd

1213
01:08:59,510 --> 01:09:01,350
Helwig,

1214
01:09:01,870 --> 01:09:04,120
Angelika...

1215
01:09:04,120 --> 01:09:05,340
Bernd!

1216
01:09:07,260 --> 01:09:08,720
It's not that easy.

1217
01:09:12,620 --> 01:09:14,170
I didn't mean it this way.

1218
01:09:14,930 --> 01:09:16,420
Don't you want to give me some time?

1219
01:09:17,890 --> 01:09:18,700
Yes I do.

1220
01:09:18,960 --> 01:09:20,070
Then keep it.

1221
01:09:20,320 --> 01:09:21,560
As long as you want.

1222
01:09:21,840 --> 01:09:23,200
Until that's true,

1223
01:09:23,350 --> 01:09:24,670
what's already written in there.

1224
01:09:24,940 --> 01:09:26,910
Bernd and Angelika Helwig.

1225
01:10:15,270 --> 01:10:16,720
The Macaroni!

1226
01:10:19,040 --> 01:10:20,190
Let! Let!

1227
01:10:20,190 --> 01:10:22,460
I'll take you to the police myself.

1228
01:10:22,470 --> 01:10:23,780
Let go of me!

1229
01:11:33,140 --> 01:11:34,980
Mr. assistant forster. Did you read already

1230
01:11:34,980 --> 01:11:38,130
that the italian Marcello Scalzi escaped from prison?

1231
01:11:43,650 --> 01:11:45,150
Sit there!

1232
01:11:45,410 --> 01:11:46,490
And eat!

1233
01:11:46,570 --> 01:11:47,540
Not eat.

1234
01:11:47,620 --> 01:11:48,600
Angelika.

1235
01:11:48,740 --> 01:11:50,560
Don't you have other problems now, you...

1236
01:11:50,560 --> 01:11:51,860
you stupid guy.

1237
01:11:51,860 --> 01:11:53,450
Angelika. Please bring Angelika.

1238
01:11:53,450 --> 01:11:56,960
You better think of yourself now.

1239
01:11:57,250 --> 01:11:58,150
Please.

1240
01:11:58,270 --> 01:11:59,530
Angelika.

1241
01:11:59,890 --> 01:12:02,570
All right then, I bring her here, you fool, (you).

1242
01:12:43,210 --> 01:12:44,810
Attention.

1243
01:12:45,030 --> 01:12:46,910
The Linz Police Department reports

1244
01:12:46,910 --> 01:12:50,510
that the italian foreign worker Marcello Scalzi escaped.

1245
01:12:50,730 --> 01:12:52,150
It's suspected

1246
01:12:52,200 --> 01:12:54,930
that he proceeds toward Kaprun, his last whereabouts.

1247
01:12:55,050 --> 01:12:55,970
Over and out.

1248
01:13:06,910 --> 01:13:07,760
Angelina.

1249
01:13:07,760 --> 01:13:09,330
You shouldn't have done that.

1250
01:13:09,570 --> 01:13:10,600
Not allowed.

1251
01:13:10,730 --> 01:13:12,250
Forbidden. Always not allowed.

1252
01:13:12,250 --> 01:13:13,620
That makes everything worse.

1253
01:13:13,620 --> 01:13:15,620
Och, not worse than locked up.

1254
01:13:15,770 --> 01:13:17,080
Always only your letters.

1255
01:13:17,080 --> 01:13:18,470
Paper, paper!

1256
01:13:19,160 --> 01:13:20,530
You come with me.

1257
01:13:20,530 --> 01:13:21,070
Now.

1258
01:13:21,070 --> 01:13:23,070
How do you imagine that, Marcello?

1259
01:13:23,150 --> 01:13:24,420
Imagine later.

1260
01:13:24,550 --> 01:13:25,570
Come now.

1261
01:13:25,820 --> 01:13:27,360
You and I belong together.

1262
01:13:27,360 --> 01:13:28,150
No.

1263
01:13:28,420 --> 01:13:31,460
You only think that, if you love one another, because you want it to be.

1264
01:13:31,460 --> 01:13:33,340
Oh, I understand.

1265
01:13:33,520 --> 01:13:34,960
You think of me as a murderer.

1266
01:13:35,030 --> 01:13:36,550
No, that's not it.

1267
01:13:36,800 --> 01:13:38,550
Please try to understand me.

1268
01:13:38,880 --> 01:13:39,740
Love...

1269
01:13:40,030 --> 01:13:42,290
is something different than living your life together.

1270
01:13:42,360 --> 01:13:44,490
I don't understand. You come with me. Now!

1271
01:13:45,200 --> 01:13:46,010
No!

1272
01:13:46,990 --> 01:13:48,070
Marcello!

1273
01:13:48,390 --> 01:13:49,360
Understand me!

1274
01:13:49,360 --> 01:13:50,940
I cannot understand.

1275
01:13:52,740 --> 01:13:55,270
Marcello, we didn't know enough about each other.

1276
01:13:55,270 --> 01:13:57,470
Why didn't you tell me back then about Tina?

1277
01:13:58,160 --> 01:13:59,120
Tina?

1278
01:13:59,660 --> 01:14:01,860
We both dreamt a beautiful dream.

1279
01:14:02,250 --> 01:14:05,220
A romantic fortune. Somewhere on an island.

1280
01:14:05,580 --> 01:14:07,940
But this island for two people alone doesn't exist.

1281
01:14:08,300 --> 01:14:09,870
You can't live dreams.

1282
01:14:10,480 --> 01:14:12,100
You must live reality.

1283
01:14:12,520 --> 01:14:15,610
And my reality is here. And yours, Tina.

1284
01:14:18,790 --> 01:14:20,730
Visitors, Gustl?

1285
01:14:21,290 --> 01:14:22,450
If a had visitors,

1286
01:14:22,740 --> 01:14:24,890
I wouldn't sit out here alone.

1287
01:14:25,260 --> 01:14:26,930
But the dog smells something.

1288
01:14:27,930 --> 01:14:29,550
Well then ask the dog,

1289
01:14:29,690 --> 01:14:31,460
if you believe it more then me.

1290
01:14:31,460 --> 01:14:32,760
You must go.

1291
01:14:32,950 --> 01:14:35,030
Try to get through to Italy.

1292
01:14:35,130 --> 01:14:36,090
Home.

1293
01:14:36,260 --> 01:14:38,320
[Italian]

1294
01:14:38,570 --> 01:14:39,440
Quick.

1295
01:14:39,440 --> 01:14:40,430
[Italian]

1296
01:14:41,260 --> 01:14:43,080
We may come in for a schnapps, may we not?

1297
01:14:43,960 --> 01:14:45,640
What are you looking for anyway?

1298
01:14:45,890 --> 01:14:48,640
Perhaps the ram you never hit.

1299
01:14:48,880 --> 01:14:49,940
Possible.

1300
01:14:49,940 --> 01:14:52,610
And what happens if I won't let you in?

1301
01:14:52,750 --> 01:14:54,950
Then we enter without the landlords admission.

1302
01:15:00,640 --> 01:15:01,250
Bella.

1303
01:15:02,300 --> 01:15:03,090
You?

1304
01:15:03,120 --> 01:15:04,880
He sensed me and gave me away.

1305
01:15:05,240 --> 01:15:07,230
But that was not very gallant of you.

1306
01:15:12,210 --> 01:15:13,460
Visitors after all?

1307
01:15:14,900 --> 01:15:17,550
You're still allowed to make fun of a hunter, aren't you?

1308
01:15:17,740 --> 01:15:18,940
And furthermore,

1309
01:15:19,390 --> 01:15:21,460
a gentleman has to...

1310
01:15:21,570 --> 01:15:22,940
keep his mouth shut.

1311
01:15:24,940 --> 01:15:25,800
Well then,

1312
01:15:25,930 --> 01:15:27,150
because you are here already,

1313
01:15:28,100 --> 01:15:29,160
let's have...

1314
01:15:29,240 --> 01:15:30,800
a schnapps, eh?

1315
01:15:51,820 --> 01:15:53,170
He must have been here.

1316
01:15:53,240 --> 01:15:54,670
Yes and has got a weapon now.

1317
01:15:54,820 --> 01:15:56,070
Yes, but...

1318
01:15:56,580 --> 01:15:58,020
only blanks.

1319
01:16:12,630 --> 01:16:13,580
Come Bella.

1320
01:16:21,770 --> 01:16:22,720
Bernd?

1321
01:16:22,770 --> 01:16:23,330
Where to?

1322
01:16:23,330 --> 01:16:25,070
The trace is still fresh. The dog is going to find him.

1323
01:16:25,120 --> 01:16:26,860
That's not our business, and yours even less.

1324
01:16:26,910 --> 01:16:27,990
An escaped prisoner...

1325
01:16:27,990 --> 01:16:30,630
Is this about a prisoner or late revenge?

1326
01:16:31,690 --> 01:16:33,470
Come, let's notify the police.

1327
01:16:37,620 --> 01:16:39,650
Tow men to the bridge and you with me.

1328
01:17:20,810 --> 01:17:22,530
He must have come over the mountains.

1329
01:17:23,040 --> 01:17:26,200
In my opinion, he tries to escape across the italian border.

1330
01:17:26,750 --> 01:17:28,800
We stay alert, naturally.

1331
01:17:29,270 --> 01:17:31,490
But I recommend to close off the passes in the south.

1332
01:17:32,530 --> 01:17:34,120
He certainly isn't here anymore.

1333
01:17:37,530 --> 01:17:38,600
You were right.

1334
01:17:38,600 --> 01:17:40,760
Now I'm almost glad he succeeded.

1335
01:17:40,760 --> 01:17:43,600
It's better for everybody. For you, for him and for Angelika.

1336
01:18:24,570 --> 01:18:25,420
You!

1337
01:18:25,420 --> 01:18:27,170
What the dog smells isn't game.

1338
01:18:30,520 --> 01:18:31,350
Marcello.

1339
01:18:31,650 --> 01:18:32,870
Be reasonable, Scalzi.

1340
01:18:32,870 --> 01:18:34,560
Attention. He is got a weapon.

1341
01:18:35,000 --> 01:18:36,910
Away! Away!

1342
01:18:37,720 --> 01:18:38,750
Go away.

1343
01:18:38,970 --> 01:18:39,980
AWAY!

1344
01:18:40,540 --> 01:18:41,810
I shoot you!

1345
01:18:42,840 --> 01:18:43,500
Bella!

1346
01:19:43,660 --> 01:19:45,000
Bella, come!

1347
01:19:48,090 --> 01:19:49,420
Bella, here!

1348
01:19:56,050 --> 01:19:57,140
Bella, come!

1349
01:20:09,900 --> 01:20:11,690
The dog could tell that,

1350
01:20:11,690 --> 01:20:12,810
if he talked.

1351
01:20:12,960 --> 01:20:14,340
But the tale

1352
01:20:14,480 --> 01:20:16,370
is not finished yet.

1353
01:20:20,490 --> 01:20:21,490
Yes...

1354
01:20:21,730 --> 01:20:23,300
Each bad weather...

1355
01:20:23,380 --> 01:20:24,620
clears up sometime.

1356
01:20:24,990 --> 01:20:26,910
And then the sun comes out.

1357
01:20:27,440 --> 01:20:28,660
Yes, Bella.

1358
01:20:29,150 --> 01:20:30,750
Bella Piccolina.

1359
01:20:32,020 --> 01:20:35,620
We still have unfinished business, Bella.

1360
01:20:36,120 --> 01:20:37,090
Come.

1361
01:20:51,530 --> 01:20:52,700
There, go.

1362
01:20:54,480 --> 01:20:56,250
There she is,

1363
01:20:56,400 --> 01:20:58,050
Bella.
